Classify this email reply from a Philippine business:

From: {{ $json.from }}
Subject: {{ $json.subject }}
Body: {{ $json.text || $json.snippet }}

Return JSON only:
{"intent": "interested|not_interested|auto_reply|unsubscribe|other", "sentiment": "positive|neutral|negative", "suggested_action": "schedule_call|send_followup|remove_from_list|no_action", "urgency": "high|medium|low", "summary": "one line summary"}

